# Patterns lychee should skip.
# - localhost / loopback URLs are expected in docs (example servers).
^https?://localhost(:\d+)?(/|$)
^https?://127\.0\.0\.1(:\d+)?(/|$)
^https?://0\.0\.0\.0(:\d+)?(/|$)

# - placeholder hostnames in examples.
your-server\.example
byo\.yourdomain\.com
example\.com

# - Discord invite is a placeholder until the server is created (Part I item 6).
discord\.gg/loovie$

# - GHCR image links resolve only once images are published (Phase A.8).
ghcr\.io/looviehq/loovie-server

# - RunPod template deep-link contains a placeholder TEMPLATE_ID until the
#   template is published in RunPod's catalog (Part I item 1).
runpod\.io/console/deploy\?template=<TEMPLATE_ID>
